================================================================================
                         TECHNOLOGY STACK
================================================================================

  Frontend:     HTML5, CSS3 (Vanilla), JavaScript (ES6)
  Backend:      Supabase (BaaS - Backend as a Service)
  Database:     PostgreSQL (via Supabase)
  Auth:         Supabase Auth (Email/Password + Google OAuth)
  AI Chatbot:   OpenRouter.ai (Gemini 2.5 Flash)
  Hosting:      Firebase Hosting (Static)
  Fonts:        Google Fonts (Inter)
  Icons:        Material Icons Round
  Animation:    anime.js + Custom CSS

================================================================================
                     MULTILINGUAL & THEME SUPPORT
================================================================================

  Languages:    English (EN) | Bahasa Melayu (MS)
  Themes:       Day Mode | Night Mode (toggle)
  Storage:      localStorage (wedrive-lang, wedrive-theme)

